{"tid":38861,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"你會同死咗嘅自己講啲咩？","createTime":"2016-12-14T07:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T07:55:50.000Z","uid":40330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c7890e4617797fc11c04bea917071d3ba28ed265","tid":38861,"uid":40330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:53:42.000Z","msg":"如果宜家你眼前有個棺材 入面瞓嗰個係你自己 你會同佢講啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n如果你係講：「你係一個好老公、好爸爸」<br />\n你宜家有冇花多啲時間去陪伴你嘅屋企人呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果你係講：「你嘅一生充滿歡樂」<br />\n咁就唔好愁眉苦臉啦 笑多啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你係講：「你嘅一生真係好精彩」<br />\n咁當你感到灰心喪志嘅時候 諗一諗呢句說話<br />\n<br />\n人一出世就步向死亡<br />\n雖然死亡係必然嘅事實<br />\n雖然有好多野我地冇辦法改變<br />\n但好希望可以同大家一齊反思下<br />\n諗下可以創造一個點樣嘅人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 第一次出post唔知放咩台 純粹呢幾日好灰 想鼓勵下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先：「你依然都係以前嗰個細路女 不忘初心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」"},{"pid":"9fe8d907f975bd12d152b3b76c333dd52efb7c99","tid":38861,"uid":660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:53:56.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"e267c399858e6d5092fe28d5dcfc2626a9830ef9","tid":38861,"uid":3682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:54:52.000Z","msg":"點解會投錯胎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15fd5c99cf707da0cca65bdb7c11e6e47c3891e2","tid":38861,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"一早應該死"}]}